title: #207 - Roy Wood Jr. & ME
description: Comedian & Daily Show Correspondent Roy Wood Jr. & I hang out in my hotel room in New York & talk about his grass root start in Comedy, working on Sullivan and Son, their tour, it's cancelation, and how he booked the Daily Show.
